pi-rules

This package implements rule/context loading for the pi coding-agent extension ecosystem.
Its behavior is inspired by oh-my-openagent (omo) at
https://github.com/code-yeongyu/oh-my-openagent, including omo's `.omo/rules/`
workflow and the rules-injector hook architecture. omo is originally licensed under
the Sustainable Use License 1.0.

